title: Seamless (or Nearly Seamless) Knits
description: Anyone who loves to knit--but doesn't love the finishing--can now enjoy all the fun parts and escape the tedium. Discover stylish projects cleverly designed for knitting either all in one piece or in sections added on by simply picking up stitches.* Enjoy 19 flattering women's garments in sizes from Small to 2XL* Find everything from a sassy sleeveless dress to cardigans, pullovers, and vests* Use a variety of stitches and techniques, including cables, textured knitting, colorwork, and entrelac
